138
00:09:09,442 --> 00:09:10,483
And there were legal wrangles.

139
00:09:10,583 --> 00:09:12,223
But it was fine for us.

140
00:09:12,704 --> 00:09:14,464
But don't do what we did.

141
00:09:17,021 --> 00:09:21,348
And also, royalties are great, but they don't always work out,

142
00:09:21,528 --> 00:09:23,872
so make sure your cash flow works without the royalties.

